[person]person_267|Werner[/person] and most of his disciples considering
them as [underline]veins of [chemical]chemical_092|Granite[/chemical][/underline] attempts to show
that they are [chemical]chemical_092|Granite[/chemical] of a different kind
from that which forms the first of the
